item.title: Olive Garden Pasta Pass
item.author: Nathan Petersen
item.description: I ate at Olive Garden 25 times in 8 weeks. You might be wondering: why did I do this, how could I afford it, did I get fat, if I am tired of pasta, or even if I am crazy? Keep reading for the answers as I attempt to explain my experience with the Olive Garden Pasta Pass.
